Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.94,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To live is continuously to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:55.53,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.28,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}繋がってる　確かなパス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.87,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your power still flows into me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}感じてる　大切なものをこの肩に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}きみとならFly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:12.67,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I decided to become a sage of the stars, oh like you
