Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh oh (Flyin’ high!! Fl- Flyin’ high!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.72,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}止まる事ない二つのタイムライン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}変えていく　さあ二人でRight now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.81,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.06,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What can I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.15,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Go on! Go on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:33.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}何処までもきみとFly
